data.title: How to remember the classification of Phylum Echinoderms ?
data.meta_description: Following are the PHylum Echinoderms, how to remember them :  Asteroidea (sea stars)   ...  or feather stars)  Holothuroidea (sea cucumbers)
data.text:
Here is a simple trick to remember the classification of Phylum Ehcinoderms:

An ECHO

An - Asteroidea

E - Echinoidea

C - Crinoidea

H - Holothuroidea

O - Ophiuroidea
